# Group Dragon

## Dragon [/dragon/create]

### Create dragon [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                'name': 'Azreal',
                'aspect': 'chaos'
            }

    + Headers

            Authentication: Bearer <token>

+ Response 422 (application/json)

    Returned when provided data is invalid

    + Body

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                'name': 'Azreal',
                'aspect': 'chaos',
                'owner': '8c08e52a-92b9-4fd3-aeb2-91d08aad7e6f',
                'gender': 'male',
                'level': 0,
                'fed': false,
                'born': 2017-10-26T16:51:59.000Z,
            }

## Dragon [/dragon/feed/{dragon_id}]

### Feed dragon [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Parameters

        + dragon_id: '8c08e52a-92b9-4fd3-aeb2-91d08aad7e6f' (required, string)

    + Body

            {
            'food': 'meat'
            }

+ Response 400 (application/json)

    Returned when dragon was not fed with appropriate reason

    + Body

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    Dragon has been fed, return updated dragon object

    + Body

## Dragon [/dragon/task]

### Send dragon on task [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authentication: Bearer <token>

    + Body

            You need to specify which dragon to send,
            provide a duration (in hours between 1 and 8), and location

            {
                dragonId: 'd3317d5f-df85-4f7e-a4f0-f1d26fb0e594',
                duration: '2',
                location: 'Githan Volcano'
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                startTime: 'Thu May 17 2018 13:19:44 GMT+0200 (Central European Daylight Time)',
                endTime: 'Thu May 17 2018 15:19:44 GMT+0200 (Central European Daylight Time)' 
            }

+ Response 400

    Received when there was an error setting the task
    or selected dragon was busy (with appropriate error)

    + Body

+ Response 422

    Received when there was an error validating data

    + Body

## Dragon [/dragon/{id}]

+ Parameters

